title: Holland and Barrett - Headington
description: Part of a chain and offers many vegetarian and vegan products. Soya and non dairy milks, munchie bars, sweets, supplements, vegan sausages and burgers, meat substitutes, dried fruit, cereals, muesli, organic stuff. A discount is given on production of a Veg Soc card. Other Oxford branches are at Cowley Centre (Templars Square), Summertown, Westgate Center and off Cornmarket in the city center - products vary store from store.
